    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches, several large dents, and peeling clear coat, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and a persistent musty odor. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there are several undiagnosed leaks and suspension noises that will need immediate repair. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it is recommended that any potential buyer brings a trailer for transport.",
